Gong Bu , a stance in Wushu and other Chinese martial arts
Gongbu joined the People 's Liberation Army in 1956 , and joined a mountaineering team in 1958 , consisting of both Chinese and Soviet mountaineers .
In 2015 , the Dallas Cowboys became the first sports team to be valued at $ 4 billion , making it the most valuable sports team in the world , according to Forbes .
They were the first professional e-sports team to consist of members from multiple continents when they formed the team from highly experienced players from Norway , Canada and United States .
The Cowboys also generated $ 620 million in revenue in 2014 , a record for a U.S. sports team .
They were also the first e-sports team ever to pay for a player transfer out of a contract when they bought Ola `` element '' Moum out of his contract with SK Gaming .
